<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Data CreatedBy="admin" CreatedOn="634130859265578915" UpdatedBy="admin" UpdatedOn="634130859855426440">
  <Properties />
  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>The example contains the two Employer and Employees groups. The 'User1' list view item is assigned to 'Employer' group. 'User2', 'User3' and 'User4' list view items are assigned to Employees group.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui ListView contains collection of groups and collection of items.  Each ListView item has the Group property to determine the group.  If group isn't set for an item, the item is related to default group.  To use groups in a ListView, you should populate Groups collection for the ListView and set specific group for each item Group property.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>
